data.description:
Boutique, gated community - The Oaks at Oakland Forest 

3 / 2.5 Townhouse with one car garage 

Available MARCH 10
 HOA screening application takes about 3 weeks to process

Great location; just off I95 and just minutes from the beach, downtown Fort Lauderdale (Las Olas) and Wilton Manors!

REQUIREMENTS:

Minimum of 650+ TransUnion FICO credit score
 
Check your score on myfico.com. No exceptions on credit. No cosigners.
**Max of 2 cars allowed**
Pet-friendly; large dogs ok. Powerful breeds such as Pitbulls, Rottweilers, German Shepards, and Presa Canarios are not allowed.
Clear background check 
Proof of a combined income of 3x the monthly rent 
No evictions 

MOVE-IN COSTS: 
3x the rent (first months rent, last months rent, and security deposit)
$150 application fee
Utilities are not included 
Free alarm monitoring service (as long as you have an active landline in your name)

FEATURES: 
Full washer and dryer on 2nd floor 
Built 2006 
Tile and laminate wood throughout
High ceilings 
Recess lighting
Spacious open design
Patio (not fenced) 
Central air 
Storage area in the garage 
Community pool 

Other rental listings:

No real estate agents. Contact JARRED
